Ya Tuhan.

47
00:03:04,875 --> 00:03:06,833
Tidak.

48
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,499
Aku mohon.

49
00:03:08,667 --> 00:03:10,875
Aku tahu kelakuanku buruk.

50
00:03:11,042 --> 00:03:13,001
Aku tahu aku sedang dihukum.

51
00:03:13,168 --> 00:03:15,209
Aku tahu.

52
00:03:15,377 --> 00:03:17,710
Aku layak menerimanya.

53
00:03:17,878 --> 00:03:19,294
Aku jahat.

54
00:03:22,503 --> 00:03:24,170
Tolong aku.
Tunjukkan aku jalannya.

55
00:03:24,337 --> 00:03:26,670
Ayo, beri tahu aku apa
yang harus kulakukan.

56
00:03:26,838 --> 00:03:28,336
Beri tahu aku.

57
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,421
Tuhan!

58
00:03:44,133 --> 00:03:46,007
Tak apa-apa.

59
